Package: tqr
Type: Package
Title: Add tq_xx functions to tidyquant package to facilitate economic analyses
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Mitsuo Shiota
Maintainer: Mitsuo Shiota <mitsuoxv@gmail.com>
Description: Add utility functions to facilitate economic analyses on
    time series data to tsibble and tidyquant packages.
    Added functions are to calculate differences (tq_diff), 
    moving averages (tq_ma), growth rates (tq_gr) and 
    seasonally adjusted values (tq_sa).
Depends: R (>= 3.5.3)
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    tidyr,
    dplyr,
    purrr,
    lubridate,
    seasonal,
    magrittr,
    tsibble,
    tibble,
    zoo,
    xts
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: 
    knitr,
